GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_WhatDoesItDo> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_WhatDoesItDo> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#WhatDoesItDo> ;
    narr:childCount "20"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "59bd5ed36ac352bb25334d8e26ac6e9f09b65516" ;
    narr:narration """This hub maps the functional and rhetorical architecture of As Written, a [git-native organizational memory tool](narr:Observation_AsWrittenProduct) designed to [extract undocumented expert knowledge](narr:Observation_WhatDoesItDo_1) into a version-controlled worldview. The product’s value proposition is validated through a [three-beat demo](narr:StyleObs_BoldBeats) that moves from [cold delegation](narr:Observation_Beat1_ColdDelegation) to [citation-backed truth](narr:Observation_Beat2_CitationLayer) and finally [epistemic gap honesty](narr:Observation_Beat3_GapHonesty). This process centers on the user [querying their own worldview](narr:Narrative_MemoryAsWitness) in real time. 

Beyond the product, the hub documents a rigorous [rhetorical style](narr:StyleObs_7) characterized by [imperative, direct-address framing](narr:StyleObs_AmbientQuote) and [compressed, arrow-chained process flows](narr:StyleObs_ArrowChainFlow). While the [V1 UX vision](narr:Obs_V1UXVision) prioritizes GitHub as infrastructure, there remains an acknowledged [gap in explaining the actual organizational workflow](narr:Obs_HowItWorksGap) beyond the technical architecture. The narrative persists as a dual-track record: the product’s mechanics and the deliberate, high-conviction performance of the pitch itself.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Narrative_MemoryAsWitness> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_HowItWorksGap> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_V1UXVision> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_AsWrittenProduct> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_Beat1_ColdDelegation> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_Beat2_CitationLayer> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_Beat3_GapHonesty> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_ExtractionExplainer> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_RememberAsConcept> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_VouchSSoT> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_WhatDoesItDo_1> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_7> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AmbientQuote> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ArrowChainFlow> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BoldBeats> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_BulletedConsequences> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DontGiveThemAnOut> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_ExtractionPlainLanguage> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_Metaphor_CollapseDistinction> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_VerbChoice_Extract> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "the application has the problem (clear), the benefit (clear), and the tech architecture (clear) — but is missing how the actual workflow within an organization works." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Obs_HowItWorksGap> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "Don't give them an out before they need one." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_DontGiveThemAnOut> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "You don't have to open a new tool. You're just using Claude Code... And in the middle of your current work, it's like, you should save that" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_AmbientQuote> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "This is my life's work." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_7> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The product is framed as a conceptual 'remember' feature rather than a live tool in early calls." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_RememberAsConcept> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The workflow relies on manual narrative seeding (Vouch) as a precursor to automated extraction." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Observation_VouchSSoT> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The pitch employs 'quality gate theater' as a dismissive framing of competing process patterns." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#StyleObs_7> ] ;
